## 阶段2：光谱数字化与标准库构建
### 2.1 像素坐标转真实光谱数据
```dart
// 1. 转换为(波长, 吸光度)数据对
List<Map<String, double>> rawSpectrum = [];
for (Point p in curvePixels) {
  double wavelength = 200 + (p.x - x0) * nmPerPixel;
  double absorbance = 4.5 - (p.y - y0) * absorbancePerPixel;
  // 过滤超出坐标轴范围的点
  if (wavelength >= 200 && wavelength <= 700 && absorbance >= 0 && absorbance <= 4.5) {
    rawSpectrum.add({"wavelength": wavelength, "absorbance": absorbance});
  }
}

// 2. 线性插值为均匀间隔（1nm/点，与标准库对齐）
List<double> uniformSpectrum = List.filled(501, 0.0); // 200-700nm共501个点
for (int i = 0; i < 501; i++) {
  double targetWavelength = 200 + i.toDouble();
  // 找到左右两个最近的点进行线性插值
  int leftIndex = rawSpectrum.lastIndexWhere((p) => p["wavelength"]! <= targetWavelength);
  int rightIndex = leftIndex + 1;
  if (leftIndex < 0 || rightIndex >= rawSpectrum.length) continue;
  
  double leftW = rawSpectrum[leftIndex]["wavelength"]!;
  double leftA = rawSpectrum[leftIndex]["absorbance"]!;
  double rightW = rawSpectrum[rightIndex]["wavelength"]!;
  double rightA = rawSpectrum[rightIndex]["absorbance"]!;
  
  uniformSpectrum[i] = leftA + (rightA - leftA) * (targetWavelength - leftW) / (rightW - leftW);
}

// 3. Savitzky-Golay滤波平滑（去除噪声，保留峰形）
// 推荐使用dart_savitzky_golay包，窗口大小5，多项式阶数2
List<double> smoothedSpectrum = savitzkyGolay(uniformSpectrum, windowSize: 5, polynomialOrder: 2);
```

### 2.2 标准光谱库构建（识别准确率的基础）
#### 数据来源
1. 优先：用实验室分光光度计测量常见农药的标准溶液（与用户检测条件一致：溶剂、浓度、温度）
2. 公开数据库：NIST Chemistry WebBook、PubChem、中国农药信息网
3. 第三方：购买商业农药光谱数据库

#### 标准库格式（JSON，放在assets目录）
```json
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "吡虫啉",
    "cas": "138261-41-3",
    "wavelengthRange": [200, 700],
    "absorbances": [2.65, 2.89, 3.12, ..., 0.01] // 长度501，对应200-700nm
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "毒死蜱",
    "cas": "2921-88-2",
    "wavelengthRange": [200, 700],
    "absorbances": [1.23, 1.45, 1.67, ..., 0.02]
  }
]
```

#### 加载标准库
```dart
import 'dart:convert';
import 'package:flutter/services.dart';

class PesticideSpectrum {
  final int id;
  final String name;
  final String cas;
  final List<double> absorbances;

  PesticideSpectrum({required this.id, required this.name, required this.cas, required this.absorbances});

  factory PesticideSpectrum.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
    return PesticideSpectrum(
      id: json['id'],
      name: json['name'],
      cas: json['cas'],
      absorbances: List<double>.from(json['absorbances']),
    );
  }
}

// 全局加载
List<PesticideSpectrum> standardLibrary = [];

Future<void> loadStandardLibrary() async {
  String jsonString = await rootBundle.loadString('assets/standard_spectra.json');
  List<dynamic> jsonList = json.decode(jsonString);
  standardLibrary = jsonList.map((json) => PesticideSpectrum.fromJson(json)).toList();
}
```

