## 阶段3：相似度匹配与识别逻辑
### 3.1 核心相似度算法（皮尔逊相关系数，最适合吸收光谱）
**原理**：计算两个光谱曲线的线性相关程度，值越接近1，相似度越高
```dart
double pearsonCorrelation(List<double> x, List<double> y) {
  if (x.length != y.length) throw ArgumentError("光谱长度必须一致");
  int n = x.length;
  
  double sumX = 0.0;
  double sumY = 0.0;
  double sumXY = 0.0;
  double sumX2 = 0.0;
  double sumY2 = 0.0;
  
  for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
    sumX += x[i];
    sumY += y[i];
    sumXY += x[i] * y[i];
    sumX2 += x[i] * x[i];
    sumY2 += y[i] * y[i];
  }
  
  double numerator = n * sumXY - sumX * sumY;
  double denominator = sqrt((n * sumX2 - sumX * sumX) * (n * sumY2 - sumY * sumY));
  
  return denominator == 0 ? 0.0 : numerator / denominator;
}
```

### 3.2 识别逻辑
```dart
class RecognitionResult {
  final String name;
  final String cas;
  final double confidence; // 相关系数，0-1

  RecognitionResult({required this.name, required this.cas, required this.confidence});
}

List<RecognitionResult> recognizePesticide(List<double> unknownSpectrum) {
  List<RecognitionResult> results = [];
  
  for (PesticideSpectrum standard in standardLibrary) {
    double correlation = pearsonCorrelation(unknownSpectrum, standard.absorbances);
    results.add(RecognitionResult(
      name: standard.name,
      cas: standard.cas,
      confidence: correlation,
    ));
  }
  
  // 按置信度降序排序
  results.sort((a, b) => b.confidence.compareTo(a.confidence));
  
  // 过滤低置信度结果
  return results.where((r) => r.confidence >= 0.9).toList();
}
```

**⚠️ 关键参数**
- 置信度阈值建议设为0.9，低于此值提示"未识别到已知农药"
- 可同时计算欧氏距离和余弦相似度，取三者交集提高准确率
- 若Top1和Top2的置信度差小于0.05，提示"可能为混合农药"

